room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Charlotte in Charlotte
review: Tried the Museum Heist room today and it was great (and difficult). Seth was very friendly and helpful, and even walked us through the end even though we ran out of time. We’ve had fun all three times we’ve gone and would definitely recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Charlotte in Charlotte
review: We had a great time!  Museum heist room was challenging and full of surprises. Jessica was a great game master!

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Charlotte in Charlotte
review: Awesome place. On my first visit we were soooo close to beating the Kidnapping room. My second visit we did the Museum Heist and passed with 3 seconds to spare with only 3 people!

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Charlotte in Charlotte
review: Went here for my 16 birthday party and it was a blast! Jessica was super nice and gave us hints when we needed them.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Charlotte in Charlotte
review: Perfect! Museum Heist was challenging and exciting. The staff were great to work with.
